description.en: In the large maritime fishery market, various application system in the field of maritime fishery focus on fund circulation and settlement. Trans-regional production, circulation and transaction need a trustworthy and stable transaction channel and currency with credibility and effective circulation. And on the basis of it, a consortium chain focuses on three-dimensional maritime fishery oriented to clothing, food, housing, transportation, tourism, shopping and entertainment and thin-center-based economic circulating system are to be built. Therefore, OceanChain is born at the right moment.
